OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FRichard Parker spoke exclusively to
OL,7,FITV News Central about who he thinks
OL,8,Fis responsible for the Birmingham bin
OL,9,Fstrikes still not being resolved.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Mayor Richard Parker has
OL,12,Fcriticised Birmingham City Council
OL,13,Fofficials, accusing them of slowing
OL,14,Fefforts to end the long-running bin
OL,15,Fstrike.
OL,17,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News
OL,18,FCentral, Labour's Parker said the
OL,19,Fprocess had been undermined by
OL,20,F"frustration, obfuscation and delay".
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/17
