OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FCommissioners were brought in by the
OL,7,FConservative government after the
OL,8,Fcouncil declared effective bankruptcy
OL,9,Fin 2023. Part of their role is to
OL,10,Fimprove industrial relations, though
OL,11,Fsome believe relations have only
OL,12,Fworsened.
OL,14,FITV News Central understands officials
OL,15,Fargued they couldn't include one-off
OL,16,Fcompensation payments in any deal with
OL,17,Fstriking workers, amid fears the
OL,18,Fcouncil could face wider equal pay
OL,19,Fclaims or be unable to afford similar
OL,20,Fpayouts to other staff.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FLead Commissioner Tony McArdle said:
OL,7,F"Commissioners have long been
OL,8,Fconcerned at the lack of contact
OL,9,Fbetween the Council and Unite. We have
OL,10,Fpushed the Council to have a plan for
OL,11,Fresolving this dispute that would make
OL,12,Fnegotiations with Unite viable.
OL,14,F"That pressure helped get the two
OL,15,Fparties to discussions at a political
OL,16,Flevel. We will continue to assist the
OL,17,FCouncil in seeking a negotiated
OL,18,Fsettlement to this dispute... We share
OL,19,Fthe frustration that this has gone on
OL,20,Ffor too long."
OL,26,@oD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
