PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FThe Lib Dems say it's a cheap shot to
OL,7,Fblame officers, pointing out that
OL,8,FLabour has been in control at every
OL,9,Flevel of government throughout the
OL,10,Fstrike.
OL,12,FQuestions have previously been raised
OL,13,Fabout whether officers are acting in
OL,14,Fline with the priorities of elected
OL,15,Fcouncillors.
OL,17,FFormer council leader John Clancy
OL,18,Fstood down in 2017 following criticism
OL,19,Fof his handling of industrial action
OL,20,Fby refuse workers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
