PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FHe said: "I'm not at all surprised,
OL,7,Fit's happened before, it happened to
OL,8,Fme. Officers of Birmingham City
OL,9,FCouncil are essentially refusing to
OL,10,Fcarry out the lawful instructions of
OL,11,Fthe political leadership.
OL,13,F"They don't see the leader in the
OL,14,Fcabinet as being their master. They
OL,15,Fsee their master as the permanent
OL,16,Fsecretary in London, the faceless
OL,17,Fbureaucrats in the local government
OL,18,Festablishment elite who are actually
OL,19,Frunning Birmingham at the moment."
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/17
