CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FSome critics of Clancy argue officers
OL,7,Fwere right to challenge aspects of his
OL,8,Fapproach, and that some of
OL,9,FBirmingham's current equal pay issues
OL,10,Fstem from decisions taken during his
OL,11,Fleadership.
OL,13,FHe insists he was undermined by
OL,14,Fofficers and that he was entitled to
OL,15,Ftry to reach a resolution with Unite
OL,16,Fthe Union.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
