CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FAhead of next week's council
OL,7,Felections, he said: "You should
OL,8,Fobviously go out and vote, but
OL,9,Factually, the impact of your vote will
OL,10,Fnot be as significant as it should be
OL,11,Fbecause officers and a chief
OL,12,Fcommissioner are in charge, and you
OL,13,Fcan't throw them out next week."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Birmingham City
OL,16,FCouncil said: "The council has a duty
OL,17,Fto act responsibly with the use of
OL,18,Ftaxpayers' money as any other council
OL,19,Fwould. We note Unite's comments in the
OL,20,Fmedia.
OL,26,@oD@UOUuD@`O]xD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
