CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,F"Any proposals to resolve the dispute
OL,7,Fmust be examined through the council's
OL,8,Fformal governance arrangements, which
OL,9,Fwill require a formal decision of the
OL,10,Fcouncil's cabinet after the 7 May
OL,11,Flocal elections."
OL,13,FThe Greens argue Labour is playing a
OL,14,Fblame game, pointing fingers at
OL,15,Feveryone but themselves and say the
OL,16,Fgovernment could remove the
OL,17,Fcommissioners if it chose to.
OL,26,@sD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
