PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FReform UK claims the situation has
OL,7,Fescalated only after its own talks
OL,8,Fwith Unite the Union, which they say
OL,9,Fhas increased pressure on Labour.
OL,11,F"This deal could have been done a lot
OL,12,Fearlier"
OL,14,FRichard Parker added, "I remain
OL,15,Fconcerned about decisions like this
OL,16,Fnot being carried out in a
OL,17,Fprofessional, rigorous way.
OL,26,@vD@WOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
