PN,37613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1777669904
OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,F"My biggest concern is that too much
OL,7,Fresponsibility for resolving this
OL,8,Fdispute resided with officers and
OL,9,Fcommissioners that, frankly, were
OL,10,Funder little to no scrutiny, didn't
OL,11,Foperate in a transparent way and,
OL,12,Ffrankly, face no jeopardy.
OL,14,F"That is one of the main underlying
OL,15,Freasons why this dispute has been left
OL,16,Funresolved for so long."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/17
