OL,3,CMayor accuses council officials of
OL,4,Champering bin strike deal
OL,6,FThe Conservatives say instead of
OL,7,Fcriticising officials who are unable
OL,8,Fto respond during the pre-election
OL,9,Fperiod, Richard Parker should explain
OL,10,Fhow much he plans to cover the council
OL,11,Ffor in potential equal pay and
OL,12,Fdiscrimination claims arising from a
OL,13,Fdeal he is reported to have helped
OL,14,Fnegotiate.
OL,16,FWatch Lewis Warner's full report on
OL,17,FITVX
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/17
